                        <condition key="other">
                           <p>The sewing has been crudely repaired with recent synthetic threads, but the original threads (of animal origin?) are still partly in place. The first text quire is missing.  </p>
                           <p>The manuscript was affected by heat and humidity. All bottom corners of the leaves are damaged with loss of some text, esp. fols. <locus from="68" to="72"/>. Text on fol. <locus target="#72v"/>is hardly readable due to strong discoloration of the parchment. Water stains in the gut of fols. <locus target="#1"/>-<locus target="#4"/>.</p>
                           
